description:
This is a 46 minute workout called '45 MIN CARDIO CALORIE BURN Treadmill Run!' from the channel IBX Running.
The workout falls under Cardio/Treadmill and Cardio/HIIT.
It's suitable for Advanced and Intermediate fitness levels.
You'll need Treadmill for this workout.
The workout has a The Endorphin Wave and The Meditative Grind vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Extreme and Challenging.

Original workout description: We are going to shred some calories today with this three part Cardio Calorie Burn treadmill workout! The three parts will be intervals, then HIIT, and lastly an endurance section. This is designed to get your heart rate high and burn some calories! Come run with Coach Rachael!

45:00 minutes of run and recovery intervals

All speeds and inclines are suggestions. Please stay safe and within your comfort zone!

Join our community of runners: http://www.ibxrunning.com
Merch: https://www.ibxrunning.com/store
IBX Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/ibxrunning/
Veronica's Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/bodibyroni/
Rachael's Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/bedopefitness/

00:00 - Intro
00:39 - Warm Up
03:39 - Workout!
43:34 - Cool Down

Workout Structure:
WARMUP: 3 minutes 
INTERVAL SECTION: (Four times)
      PUSH PACE: 2 minutes - 5.5 - 8.0 mph
      BASE PACE: 1 minute - 4.5 - 6.5 mph
HIIT SECTION: (10 times)
      HIIT: 1 minutes - 6.0 - 9.0 mph
      RECOVER: 30 seconds - 3....
